  "description": "OW-II doctrine applied: SNES SPC700 at Vertex 2 with warm echo FIR [80,30,15,8,3,0,0,0] — not the flat default [127,0,0,0,0,0,0,0]. eraMemory 4.5s holds the warm tail. eraPortamento 1.1s — the console exhales slowly. Low glitch (0.05) — one artifact every now and then, like a VHS warp. This is the sound of a console left running all night.",
